Located on the Gold Coast, BJP Analytical Laboratory offers contract GMP laboratory testing, providing analytical testing services to pharmaceutical and complimentary medicine manufacturers. With BJPs 16 and expanding professional staff, including three PhD, you have a partner who understands the unique requirements of your business and industry; one who can provide the technical expertise, innovation and world-class facilities that enable you to bring products to market faster and meet all the current quality, health and safety standards.

The TGA accredited laboratory offers analytical (including chemistry and microbiological) services for the testing of Raw Materials, In-Process Formulations, Finished Products and Formulation Stability. We follow either client-supplied methods, compendial methods or methods that we have developed and validated for clients. With extensive experience and a broad working knowledge of many dosage forms. We offer excipient testing to support USP/NF, EP, BP monograph testing requirements. We also can test following client-supplied or vendor supplied methodology. Our raw material testing supports formulation development within research and development, excipients and active pharmaceutical ingredients used in finished product manufacturing and supports the qualification of our client’s raw material vendors.
